<!-- ============== FAQ ============== -->
<section id="faq" class="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow center"><span class="dot"></span>FAQs</p>
    <h2 class="section-title center">Good questions.<br><em>Straight answers.</em></h2>

    <div class="faq-list">
      <details><summary>How does it actually work?<span class="chev" aria-hidden="true"></span></summary><p>The camera magnetically snaps into a soft silicone collar. Press the power button, press record, and it captures 1080p video to the included microSD card. Pop the card into your computer when they get home.</p></details>
      <details><summary>Will my pet even notice it?<span class="chev" aria-hidden="true"></span></summary><p>The camera weighs just a few grams — roughly the same as a small dog tag. The silicone collar is soft and pinch-free. Most pets ignore it within a few minutes.</p></details>
      <details><summary>How long does the battery last?<span class="chev" aria-hidden="true"></span></summary><p>Up to 2 hours of continuous 1080p recording. Plenty of time for a walk, a play session, or a full afternoon of cat-style window patrol. Charges back up in about 45 minutes via USB-C.</p></details>
      <details><summary>What pets can wear it?<span class="chev" aria-hidden="true"></span></summary><p>Pawlens is designed for dogs and cats roughly 8 lbs and up. The collar adjusts from a 8" to a 18" neck. Anything smaller and the camera ratio gets bulky — we don't recommend it for tiny breeds under 8 lbs.</p></details>
      <details><summary>Is it really waterproof?<span class="chev" aria-hidden="true"></span></summary><p>Yes. The camera is rated to 10 meters (about 32 ft). Rain, puddles, sprinklers, lake swims, full bath dunks — all fine. Just rinse and dry the silicone collar afterward.</p></details>
      <details><summary>Do I need WiFi or an app?<span class="chev" aria-hidden="true"></span></summary><p>No. Pawlens deliberately doesn't use WiFi or apps. It records to a microSD card. Plug it into your laptop, drag the files over, watch. That's it.</p></details>
      <details><summary>When will my order arrive?<span class="chev" aria-hidden="true"></span></summary><p>Orders ship within 24 hours from our US warehouse. Standard delivery is 3–5 business days. You'll get a tracking link as soon as it leaves.</p></details>
      <details><summary>What's the return policy?<span class="chev" aria-hidden="true"></span></summary><p>30 days, no questions asked. If your pet hates it, or you just don't love the footage, send it back for a full refund. We pay return shipping.</p></details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

